snippet.title: Part 1.5 Concept Trailer: Hailing from Nagazora and Falling into Abyss - Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
The dust in Nagazora stirred up black and white in bubbles.
The living and the dead danced together on the boundless sea surface.
An ode to the shimmering newborn.
